- Use UTF-8 when reading or writing files.
- Use robust file paths (prefer `Path(__file__).resolve().parent` for local data files).
- Handle common edge cases in data scripts:
  - empty input files
  - missing expected columns
  - blank or malformed rows
  - empty strings before `.split()` or other text operations

